Reasoning: The paper discusses user security and privacy concerns regarding wearables, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The survey conducted in the paper also touches on issues related to cybercrime (cs.CY) and social implications of technology (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the design of user notification, permission management, and access control schemes for wearables, which could fall under the category of other computer science topics (cs.OH).
